title: John Mayer Complete Discography
description:
This is a complete Discography Of John Mayer
which includes the following albums

* Room for squares
* Heavier Things
* Heavier Things (bonus Disc)
* Inside wants out
* John mayer trio house of blues
* John mayer trio Try
* Any Given Thursday
* Live In New York
* Live From Abbey Road
* Continuum
* The Village Sessions

* there is also included a collection of songs which do not fit in any albums
mostly acoustic versions of already released songs
